description.text: JoeRunner meets his friend T.T. outside the school.
description.html: JoeRunner meets his friend T.T. outside the school.

transcript.html:
The boy with black hair watches as JoeRunner walks out of a minivan with a canoe strapped to the top. The boy wears a T-shirt reading “77” and shorts, has constant dropped eyebrows, and speaks in an all-lowercase sans-serif font.

[boy] Oh, finally.

JoeRunner walks up to the boy.

[boy] Hey, JoeRunner, you made it! And it only took, like, two decades!

[JoeRunner] Yeah, there was lots of traffic on North 1 today.

The boy starts walking to the door.

[character bio] T.T. / one heck of a guy

[T.T.] Yeah, yeah, excuses, excuses. Come on! We’re only gonna have time for six games of Hyper Galactic Battle Ducks III! Six!
